<plot>Shown at the Museum of Modern Art and the International Center of Photography, this documentary short about firemen won the Schneider Award for "Most Promising Director" at the 1973 New York University Film Festival. Filmmaker Andrew Holbrooke captured the daily routines of New York City firemen on the job in East Harlem.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?317515</url></doc>
